PoxPay,is,a,payment,service,that,uses,voice,biometric,technology,to,identify,and,authorize,purchases,With,PoxPay,users,aren,t,required,to,enter,a,password,instead,using,their,voice,and,phone,as,their,password,Developers,can,integrate,PoxPay,s,authentication,features,into,their,applications,and,services,using,the,RESTful,API,Users,must,contact,the,company,to,obtain,documentation